{"tid":1919664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"福慧佛堂就佛堂內多人感染致歉","createTime":"2020-03-11T02:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T15:41:10.000Z","uid":277339,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb6dad477dd6ef23711ff1347769de06e777d2f","tid":1919664,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"北角福慧佛堂在報章刊登聲明，對佛堂出現新型冠狀病毒群組感染表示後悔難過。佛堂指在農曆新年後，曾因應疫情商討應否暫停共修，但因社會觸覺不夠靈敏，出現不同意見而作罷，回想事件感到懊悔不已。佛堂又指，對多人染病及傳媒高度關注毫無經驗，一時不知如何是好，因此與政府及傳媒配合不當表示歉意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272920&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1272920%26csid%3D261_341&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=6404fbe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272920&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b2114c845fa869a1fd316d6b089369761e919aff","tid":1919664,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4d72ada5d517c6b480d8743103c3ead25fce12f","tid":1919664,"uid":69334,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"唔需要道歉，肯幫手喺福建幫地頭社區爆發就係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a9997e2aa08df5b6a97600558889071a865dfa","tid":1919664,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"你哋冇做錯"},{"pid":"f60229abfd981543a19b82cd54083fe65016941e","tid":1919664,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"北角藍屍廢老消除計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab7